Class AbstractJavaDoc

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.zcu.validator.jdparser.api.javadocs.AbstractJavaDoc
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Commentable, Deprecateable, Seeable, Sinceable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaDocAttribute, JavaDocClass, JavaDocMethod

    public abstract class AbstractJavaDoc
extends java.lang.Object
implements Seeable, Sinceable, Deprecateable, Commentable
    Design pattern - Adapter. Standard JavaDoc element is able to hold this information.
    Author:
    Stepan Cais, scais@kiv.zcu.cz, 6.12.2012
